<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xml:lang="en"
      lang="en"
      metal:use-macro="context/@@main_template/master"
      i18n:domain="launchpad">

<body>

<metal:leftportlets fill-slot="portlets_one">
  <div class="portlet">
    <h4>What&#8217;s this all about? </h4>
    <div class="portletBody portletContent">      
      <img src="/++resource++info_icon.gif" />
      The change log is uploaded by the package maintainer when a new
      package release is made. It should document all the latest information
      we have for this release of the package.

    </div>
  </div>
</metal:leftportlets>

<div metal:fill-slot="main">

    <h1>ChangeLog</h1>

    <tal:block condition="context/changelog">
      <p>This is the latest changelog we have on file for this source
      package:</p>
    
      <pre>
<!-- No identation on pre structure -->
<span tal:replace="structure view/linkified_changelog" />
      </pre>
    </tal:block>

    <p tal:condition="not: context/changelog" class="portalMessage">
      There is no changelog associated with this source package.
    </p>

</div>
</body>
</html>
